Feminised cannabis seeds
Super Sativa Seed Club

The Super Sativa Seed Club has some fine quality feminised cannabis seeds, many using original 1980’s genetics during the breeding process. These are often combined with some of the best modern THC rich cannabis genetics to produce new feminised strains. The result is the very best of new school breeding combined with original old school cannabis genetics. Expect some unusual and exquisite flavours alongside rare (but wonderful) aromas with SSSC feminised strains.

Your SSSC feminised cannabis seed options include Purple OG Punch, Strawberry Chemdawg OG, Lava Freeze, Super Mad Sky Floater, TnT Trichome, Pineapple Poison, Kosher Haze, Lemon OG and Bruce Lemon Diesel. These strains offer something for every grower. Even though it is called the Super Sativa Seed Club you will find a range of fine-quality indica and hybrid strains as well as the trademark sativa selections.

The SSSC feminised cannabis seed range should produce 95%+ female plants. The strains were all selected for above average yields and are easy to grow across a wide range of grow methods/grow systems. The careful genetic selection assures very high THC levels and a rich, vibrant taste/aroma.

PREMIUM
CANNABIS SEEDS
WITH LEGENDARY
GENETICS

The Super Sativa Seed Club (SSSC) was founded in Amsterdam by Karel Schelfhout in 1985 focusing on high quality cannabis strains. His mission: to spread cannabis seeds around the world and empower cannabis consumers to grow their own cannabis from the very best genetics. The Super Sativa Seed Club received a High Times Hall of Fame award in 2007 as seed bank pioneers and legendary breeders.

A new era for craft growers has begun, enthusiasts around the world will be able to enjoy the unique experience of having the legendary genetics of the Super Sativa Seed Club, a cannabis treasure, an old school blast.
